      "message": "Because addAlpha is much faster than safelyAddAlpha: SkTMin(x, 255) is much slower than x - (x \u003e\u003e 8). However, the addAlpha can only handle 256, but not 257. safelyAddAlpha can handle any value greater than 255.",
